               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went to see a gentleman in Bond-street, and in crossing I picked up the bag, which I saw laying down; I found there were two pint pots in it - I took it up; one pot fell from it - I put it into my pocket; I went on, and found another pot; I was turning back to take it home, or to find a pot-boy; the witness then laid hold of me.</p>
